### Basic Connectivity Testing

Activate VPN and test connectivity from your workstation. This will verify that the new cluster is reachable and that the ingress controller is functioning correctly:

```bash
curl -k https://sitccm01.ingress01.sit.nl.cjscp.org.uk:443/usersgroups-service/internal/metrics/ping
```

Test from a server in the target environment (e.g., `ENVCCM01ACTAP##.cpp.nonlive`):

```bash
curl -k https://sitccm01-api-lb.sit.cpp.nonlive:443/usersgroups-service/internal/metrics/ping
```

Both should return `pong`.
